{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Bv_values.Eval</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"soteria","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Soteria","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Bv_values","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Eval","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-eval_binop\"><a href=\"#val-eval_binop\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> eval_binop : <span><a href=\"../Svalue/Binop/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.Binop.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-eval_unop\"><a href=\"#val-eval_unop\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> eval_unop : <span><a href=\"../Svalue/Unop/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.Unop.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-eval_nop\"><a href=\"#val-eval_nop\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> eval_nop : <span><a href=\"../Svalue/Nop/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.Nop.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a> list</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-eval\"><a href=\"#val-eval\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> eval : \u000A  <span><span class=\"optlabel\">?force</span>:bool <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span class=\"optlabel\">?eval_var</span>:<span>(<span><a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"../../Symex/Var/index.html#type-t\">Soteria.Symex.Var.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-ty\">Svalue.ty</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <a href=\"../Svalue/index.html#type-t\">Svalue.t</a></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Evaluates an expression; will call <code>eval_var</code> on each <code>Var</code> encountered. If evaluation errors (e.g. from a division by zero), gives up and returns the original expression. The <code>force</code> flag forces evaluation to proceed even if no sub-expressions changed (required if evaluating an expression that has not been constructed using smart constructors).</p></div></div>"}